caption: A small black toy car begins its journey across a detailed map of Northern Europe. It smoothly rolls forward, tracing a path over the intricate lines and names of countries. The car's glossy surface reflects the ambient light, creating a playful contrast against the muted colors of the map. Its wheels turn steadily, as if embarking on an adventurous road trip across the vast, printed landscape.
